perl-Curses
-------------------------------------------
Perl module which allows access to the ncurses libraries.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  libncurses8-5.5-3
  perl-5.8.7-5

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.5-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  perl-5.8.7-5

Canonical homepage:
  http://search.cpan.org/~giraffed/Curses/

Canonical download:
  http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/G/GI/GIRAFFED/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-Curses-1.16-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-Curses-1.16-1.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-Curses-1.16-1-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-Curses-1.16-1.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /etc/postinstall/perl-Curses.sh
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/Curses.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/Curses/.packlist
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/Curses/Curses.bs
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/Curses/Curses.dll
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/Curses/libCurses.dll.a
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/perl-Curses-1.16.README
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Curses-1.16/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Curses-1.16/HISTORY
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Curses-1.16/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Curses-1.16/README
  /usr/share/man/man3/Curses.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/perl/cygwin-pods/5.8/Curses.pod

