Rebuilt against perl-5.8.6.

----- version 1.08-1 -----
New upstream release, built against the libncurses8 package.
Now includes support for libform, libmenu, and libpanel.

----- version 1.07-1 -----
New release with a new upstream maintainer.  Fixes build issue included 
in previous Cygwin patches.

